{"tid":835671,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頭痛到想死","createTime":"2018-09-25T05:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T09:04:11.000Z","uid":194534,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9048b9160e5fa48ed14113e6bfbee7ed0e7bba0e","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"到底有冇人明白成日頭痛果種痛楚<br />\n由細個開始都頭痛得好密<br />\n痛既位置唔一定次次一樣<br />\n但每次都好似有野鑽緊你個頭咁<br />\n或者有人用錘仔揼緊你個頭<br />\n陰陰咁痛有時會想作嘔<br />\n好想用死去解脫頭痛<br />\n個頭就黎爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a54a3e3bdd601816ae5764586e091f9bff2a996","tid":835671,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家頭痛到仆街"},{"pid":"8deb097305b761c799d2304d1a4210b3dd9e8c34","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"我前排頭痛睇中醫，醫師同我量量血壓，先發現係低血壓"},{"pid":"efcf65b667d054882864f26a4edf754e1deb7c7a","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a54a3e3bdd601816ae5764586e091f9bff2a996","tid":835671,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家頭痛到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"長期都食止痛藥搞唔掂"},{"pid":"26b45c206fb686db0fc17f91928ff7eae4f2fd25","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8deb097305b761c799d2304d1a4210b3dd9e8c34","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"我前排頭痛睇中醫，醫師同我量量血壓，先發現係低血壓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"因為血壓低導致頭痛？"},{"pid":"70809a692802e1bb2193b776fa374e937f360458","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b45c206fb686db0fc17f91928ff7eae4f2fd25","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8deb097305b761c799d2304d1a4210b3dd9e8c34","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"我前排頭痛睇中醫，醫師同我量量血壓，先發現係低血壓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"因為血壓低導致頭痛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"係呀 你上網睇睇 低血壓病徵 講話會引致頭痛"},{"pid":"6470e73b35d1735039f9227b3d446f0fb325be1b","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26b45c206fb686db0fc17f91928ff7eae4f2fd25","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8deb097305b761c799d2304d1a4210b3dd9e8c34","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"我前排頭痛睇中醫，醫師同我量量血壓，先發現係低血壓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"因為血壓低導致頭痛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"低血壓症狀其實和高血壓的症狀部份雷同，但是頭痛及頭暈的感覺則大不相同。<br />\n可能的症狀包含：<br />\n1.會有整日頭重重的感覺，頭痛，視力模糊、頭暈、耳鳴、眩暈、暈厥。<br />\n2.臉色蒼白、虛弱、時常感到很累、想睡、疲倦，頻繁的打呵欠。<br />\n3.身體四肢無力，肩膀也會酸痛。<br />\n4.手腳冰冷如冰，注意力不佳。<br />\n5.胃部脹氣不舒服，有打嗝、食慾不振及嘔吐的情形。<br />\n6.低血壓如果惡化，可能會造成昏倒、甚至癲癇的情況發生。"},{"pid":"644947185f571fe5663ebfad7f3f2f3f4c3b1662","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6470e73b35d1735039f9227b3d446f0fb325be1b","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26b45c206fb686db0fc17f91928ff7eae4f2fd25","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8deb097305b761c799d2304d1a4210b3dd9e8c34","tid":835671,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"我前排頭痛睇中醫，醫師同我量量血壓，先發現係低血壓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"因為血壓低導致頭痛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"低血壓症狀其實和高血壓的症狀部份雷同，但是頭痛及頭暈的感覺則大不相同。<br />\n可能的症狀包含：<br />\n1.會有整日頭重重的感覺，頭痛，視力模糊、頭暈、耳鳴、眩暈、暈厥。<br />\n2.臉色蒼白、虛弱、時常感到很累、想睡、疲倦，頻繁的打呵欠。<br />\n3.身體四肢無力