、時常感到很累、想睡、疲倦，頻繁的打呵欠。<br />\n3.身體四肢無力，肩膀也會酸痛。<br />\n4.手腳冰冷如冰，注意力不佳。<br />\n5.胃部脹氣不舒服，有打嗝、食慾不振及嘔吐的情形。<br />\n6.低血壓如果惡化，可能會造成昏倒、甚至癲癇的情況發生。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"好多都中喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飲中藥你有冇好到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"有呀 不過中醫你要試用夾<br />\n唔係個個都岩自己既<br />\n你可以叫醫生（中西醫都得）同你量量會唔會有啲低血壓先<br />\n如果冇低血壓，可以再抽血驗下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"我有懷疑自己係偏頭痛<br />\n長期咁頭痛法都想去睇下醫生<br />\n好辛苦"},{"pid":"0700cc7f802b13ec66f5b7c6de2f73c2d62ddfef","tid":835671,"uid":82189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"偏頭痛係咪絕症？"},{"pid":"47726deb4e91b2902ed70bc710e4e6db204bb9a4","tid":835671,"uid":28485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"郁一郁就痛<br />\n訓低起身就心跳加速<br />\n諗起都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471fdb2de96e185963dc78d77d18accc57bb6508","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0700cc7f802b13ec66f5b7c6de2f73c2d62ddfef","tid":835671,"uid":82189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"偏頭痛係咪絕症？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:00:51.000Z","msg":"好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難搵成因"},{"pid":"e54dc0569f790e23bc8adac6bb732251903e966a","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47726deb4e91b2902ed70bc710e4e6db204bb9a4","tid":835671,"uid":28485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:09:57.000Z","msg":"郁一郁就痛<br />\n訓低起身就心跳加速<br />\n諗起都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:02:16.000Z","msg":"痛到唔會想做任何野<br />\n訓又訓唔到，食又食唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20fadb5367f564f154ecf9a7fdef97b71dda6db","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"試下早訓<br />\n同埋唔好咁多情緒波幅先"},{"pid":"9dfea876c6a8ad1e0401c30e2fd598daa7f5fda4","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20fadb5367f564f154ecf9a7fdef97b71dda6db","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"試下早訓<br />\n同埋唔好咁多情緒波幅先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"我有試過10/11點訓，又試過2/3點訓<br />\n訓多訓少都有頭痛"},{"pid":"64da6c20337d4a935a54d37e16038b9b348c8e36","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfea876c6a8ad1e0401c30e2fd598daa7f5fda4","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20fadb5367f564f154ecf9a7fdef97b71dda6db","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"試下早訓<br />\n同埋唔好咁多情緒波幅先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"我有試過10/11點訓，又試過2/3點訓<br />\n訓多訓少都有頭痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"要長時間慢慢改善<br />\n我女朋友以前都係日日頭痛肚痛<br />\n之後我迫佢每日12點前準備訓覺，訓緊果陣都唔准用手機<br />\n過左幾個月已經好左好多，幾日先痛一次，變返起碼正常少少好似頭痛先係唔尋常咁，知道可能係壓力同情緒處理唔好或者訓得差<br />\n<br />\n冇人天生就會頭痛，你可能話有人有咁既體質，但係絕對可以調理改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76923b028c14fe9387869d230a25d50729c0d310","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64da6c20337d4a935a54d37e16038b9b348c8e36","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfea876c6a8ad1e0401c30e2fd598daa7f5fda4","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20fadb5367f564f154ecf9a7fdef97b71dda6db","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:13:05.000Z","msg":"試下早訓<br />\n同埋唔好咁多情緒波幅先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"我有試過10/11點訓，又試過2/3點訓<br />\n訓多訓少都有頭痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"要長時間慢慢改善<br />\n我女朋友以前都係日日頭痛肚痛<br />\n之後我迫佢每日12點前準備訓覺，訓緊果陣都唔准用手機<br />\n過左幾個月已經好左好多，幾日先痛一次，變返起碼正常少少好似頭痛先係唔尋常咁，知道可能係壓力同情緒處理唔好或者訓得差<br />\n<br />\n冇人天生就會頭痛，你可能話有人有咁既體質，但係絕對可以調理改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"你女朋友宜家重有冇頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甩左頭痛真好<br />\n我睡眠質素係幾差，醒訓多數都唔係一教訓天光<br />\n但又唔多覺好大壓力，做野呀家庭拍拖乜事都冇<br />\n不過家族有高血壓唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ca76658b67cfe24c2a8aa973a219bb863d0a13","tid":835671,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"夜訓，亂食凍野，唔做運動"},{"pid":"ac86df25a05b64f3acef58566e1782dcde711785","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67ca76658b67cfe24c2a8aa973a219bb863d0a13","tid":835671,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"夜訓，亂食凍野，唔做運動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"之前都有跑開，呢排一個星期跑兩日步<br />\n我有試過早訓都有痛唔知係咪訓太多<br />\n我都盡量戒凍野架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都係痛"},{"pid":"de2c01fa920237333e9b579a78d8cc9e880ed4f7","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76923b028c14fe9387869d230a25d50729c0d310","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64da6c20337d4a935a54d37e16038b9b348c8e36","tid":835671,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dfea876c6a8ad1e0401c30e2fd598daa7f5fda4","tid":835671,"uid":194534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"我有試過10/11點訓，又試過2/3點訓<br />\n訓多訓少都有頭痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"要長時間慢慢改善<br />\n我女朋友以前都係日日頭痛肚痛<br />\n之後我迫佢每日12點前準備訓覺，訓緊果陣都唔准用手機<br />\n過左幾個月已經